Easy download the WhatsApp Contact
Easy Export the WhatsApp Contact

Key Features
✓ Good-looking UI
✓ 100% Free
✓ All the features are free
✓ Export the WhatsApp contact from Your Chat list
✓ Export the WhatsApp contact from Group
✓ Export the WhatsApp contact from Label

How to get started?
1. Open web.whatsapp.com and log in by scanning the QR code
2. Open the "WA Contact Exporter" extension
3. Choose the type of data you want to export
4. Click the "Export" Button
5. Click the "Download" Button

Is it free?
Yes, WA Contact Exporter is free to use.
All the features are free.

Need more features?
Contact me via email and let me know your ideas.

FAQ
If it's not working, try disabling other WhatsApp extensions and retry.
For assistance, contact us for email.

Data Privacy
All data remains on your local device and never passes through our servers.
